(3, 3, 172, 'Hotel Kailali Siddhartha, Tikapur', '503349', 'Hotel Kailali Siddhartha, Tikapur', 'hotel-kailali-siddhartha-tikapur', '2Nbuos', 'vCxyr-logo.jpg', 'Hotel & Resort', 41, '', 'YTowOnt9', 'aKL7Q-tikapur_banner.jpg', 'TZKQj-1e2a6955_1_2.jpg', '', '+977 9858424102', '+977 9858424102', '+977 9858424102', 'manager.tikapur@siddharthahospitality.com', 'manager.tikapur@siddharthahospitality.com', 'manager.tikapur@siddharthahospitality.com', '', 0, 'Tikapur,Kailali', 'pokhara', 'Gandaki', 'Kaski/Pokhara', 'Nepal', 'Prakash Karki', ' +977 61 420077', 'info@cultureresortpokhara.com', 'www.cultureresortpokhara.com', 'Ringed by verdant green hills on the side of Fewa lake, Its an amazing place infused with traditional element and blended with modern comfort.', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<div class=\"overview-img\">\r\n			<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/tikapur-restaurant.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			1 Dining and 1 Bar Available</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Opening Hour: 06 AM to 9 PM</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			20 Pax on restaurant&nbsp;</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			28 pax on dining&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Hotel Siddhartha is the first and glorious hotel run by Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality in the picturesque town of Tikapur, which is best known for its exemplary urban planning with an immaculate garden park established by the late king Mahendra. The Hotel can either be reached from Nepalgunj (116km) or Dhangadi Airport (94 km). Tucked 13km away from Lamki at the East-West Highway and 26 km away from the famous Karnali Bridge at Chisapani, the Hotel boasts open space, two gardens (Salleri and Kalki) and ample parking as well as offers spectacular view of Tikapur town and beyond. The Indian border town of Tikunia lies at 25km from the Hotel. Given the opulence of open space the Hotel is best suited for social events, BBQ parties, live music etc.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			The hotel serves authentic local foods, particularly the Tharu delicacies and banana products, besides Nepali and Indian cuisine.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/tikapur-overview2.jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		The Hotel is apparently a hub to visit tourist and recreational destinations such as, Tikapur Park (4km), Ghodaghodi Lake (36km), Karnali Bridge (26km), Dolphin Area (10km), Bardia National Park (42km), among others.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Specialty - Tikapur Park, Dolphines can be seen at river</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2021-07-16', 1, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 22, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3505.1375471489227!2d81.11232827280818!3d28.535585122051845!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39a20da7b33b1c0b%3A0x4d9e3a953395e9a7!2sHotel%20Siddhartha%2C%20Tikapur!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1702629402090!5m2!1sen!2snp', '', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '', '', 'Hotel Siddhartha is the first and glorious hotel run by Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality in the picturesque town of Tikapur, which is best known for its exemplary urban planning with an immaculate garden park established by the late king Mahendra. ', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'tikapur', 'uCTLc9'),
(4, 4, 171, 'Siddhartha River Side Resort, Chumlingtar', '503342', 'Siddhartha River Side Resort, Chumlingtar', 'siddhartha-river-side-resort-chumlingtar', 'YDMIi7', 'BXGGC-logo.jpg', 'Hotel & Resort', 12, '', 'YToxOntpOjA7czoyNToiYTI3TXMtM29pcWFfZ3JhbmRsb2dvLnBuZyI7fQ==', 'eriID-a.jpg', '9Ls5m-chumlingtar_front.jpg', '', '9851151478, 9851151479', '9851151478, 9851151479', '9851151478, 9851151479', 'chumlingtar@siddharthahospitality.com', 'chumlingtar@siddharthahospitality.com', 'chumlingtar@siddharthahospitality.com', '', 0, 'Chumlingtar,Icchakamana gaupalika -03, Chitwan', 'Kohalpur', 'Bheri', 'Banke/Nepalgunj', 'Nepal', 'Sanjay Shrestha', '+977 081 542077', 'info@hotelmaxx.com.np', 'www.hotelmaxx.com.np', 'A business Class Hotel with 4 star facilities in Kohalpur offering the best in modern amenities with traditional Nepalese hospitality', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<div class=\"overview-img\">\r\n			<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/chumlingtar-restaurant.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Munal 40 Pax, Danfe 30 Pax , lounge Bar 25 pax.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Number of Dining &amp; Bars - 3</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Opening Hours - 16</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b>Specialty -</b></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Hygiene Food in highway , Local food items</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			The Siddhartha Riverside Resort is situated on the bank of the Gushing Trishuli River at the Pritivi Highway in Chumlingtar, Chitwan. It is conveniently located from country&#39;s busiest cities, which is less than three hours&#39; comfortable drive (95kms) from Kathmandu, 99 km from Pokhara and 75 km from Chitwan National Park (Sauraha). Siddhartha Riverside Resort is an ideal retreat for everyone either lazing at the resort or engaging in outdoor activities or adventures.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Tucked away few minutes from the Mankamana Cable Car station at Kurintar, this Resort is a perfect destination for those who want to pay homage to Goddess Manakamana (the wish-fulfilling-deity) while languishing in the opulence of waters and lush green surroundings. The Resort offers every recreational facility such as Swimming Pool, Spa, Camp/Bonfire, Live BBQ, Village Hiking, among others.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/chumlingtar-overview.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2021-07-16', 1, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 21, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3527.4018377142183!2d84.6435400745013!3d27.858923976095976!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3995204b5a72f8cf%3A0x6545a2301d418f0!2sSiddhartha%20Riverside%20Resort%2C%20Chitwan!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1702629863328!5m2!1sen!2snp', 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/3Q49nhe5ffLLRsnr6', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '', '', 'The Siddhartha Riverside Resort is situated on the bank of the Gushing Trishuli River at the Pritivi Highway in Chumlingtar, Chitwan.', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/SiddharthaResortChumlingtar', '', '', 'Chumling', 'uWn3nn');
