(5, 4, 168, 'Siddhartha Boutique Hotel, Boudha', '503340', 'Siddhartha Boutique Hotel, Boudha', 'siddhartha-boutique-hotel-boudha', '9n2T4c', 'rd4g6-logo.jpg', 'Hotel & Resort', 10, '', 'YToxOntpOjA7czoyNDoiS0FhVUItYm91ZGRoYV9iYW5uZXIuanBnIjt9', 'JLS7p-img_1985_hdr_1_1.jpg', 'a8Rfw-boudha_thumbnail.jpg', '', '+977 1 4820071', '977-9851326963', '+9779851326963', 'sales.boudha@siddharthahospitality.com', 'sales.boudha@siddharthahospitality.com', 'sales.boudha@siddharthahospitality.com', '', 0, 'Simaltar, Boudha, Kathmandu', 'Banke', 'Bheri', 'Banke/Nepalgunj', 'Nepal', 'Yub Raj', ' 081410140', 'info@hotelcentralplaza.com', 'www.hotelcentralplaza.com', 'Five star hotel in Kohalpur. Best for every sort of guests; be it holidays or destination wedding, business guests or someone on the way to Kailash', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<div class=\"overview-img\">\r\n			<img src=\"/userfiles/images/bouddha_restaurant.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Enjoy the diverse and convenient culinary offerings available at our hotel. Our on-site restaurants cater to all tastes and appetites, with The Fun Caf&eacute; and The Coffee Shop serving up delicious dishes from breakfast to dinner. For a serene dining experience, head to our rooftop restaurant, The Terrace Garden.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Satisfy your sweet tooth with delightful treats at The Pastry Shop or unwind with your preferred beverage at The Lobby Bar. For those who prefer dining in the privacy of their own room, we offer 24-hour room service.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Tucked away from the bustling town, the Hotel is perched on an idyllic hillock in the vicinity of the Bouddhanath Stupa, the Buddhist centre of reverence and the World Heritage Site. It is located at 3.8 Km from the most revered Hindu temple Pashupatinath, another World Heritage Site and just few minutes&#39; walk from the Kopan Monastery. The Hotel is 4 Km drives away from Tribhuvan International Airport.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			The Hotel infuses Nepali with the Tibetan traditional architecture, offering the state-of-the-art amenities. The Hotel is apparently a gallery of Tibetan and high-land art showcasing crafted wooden furnitures, thankas (scroll paintings), woolen carpets and photographs.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_2604-HDR%20(1).jpg\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Spanning over 10 ropanis (1.25 acres) of land, the Hotel boasts a poolside restaurant, a swimming pool, a gymnasium alongside a spa, three conference-cum-banquet halls varying in size and themes and ample parking space. The rooms, balconies and the terraces of the Hotel are apparently the vantage-point to marvel at the Buddhist monasteries surrounding the Hotel as well as the city&#39;s landscape.</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Be it a quieter and contemplative stay for the spiritual pursuits or business meetings and conference, or recreational activities in the health club, the Hotel is an ideal address for all reasons.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2021-07-18', 0, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 20, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d14126.085883445201!2d85.3670872!3d27.7320575!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39eb1bc700925d0f%3A0x99d2e413244623fe!2sSiddhartha%20Boutique!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1695990372698!5m2!1sen!2snp', '', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '<di