(6, 4, 163, 'Siddhartha Hotel Grand City, Birtamode', '503343', 'Siddhartha Hotel Grand City, Birtamode', 'siddhartha-hotel-grand-city-birtamode', '4dLW7d', 'ln6Ok-d7sut_logo_himalaya.png', 'Hotel & Resort', 32, '', 'YToxOntpOjA7czoyNToiN2hFVkEtM29pcWFfZ3JhbmRsb2dvLnBuZyI7fQ==', 'Awmji-birtamod_banner.jpg', 'o2ZJg-birtamod_thumbnail.jpg', '', '+977-23-590517/18', '+977-23-590517/18', '+977-23-590517/18', 'gcity@siddharthahospitality.com', 'gcity@siddharthahospitality.com', 'gcity@siddharthahospitality.com', '', 1, 'Ujyalo Ekta Tole, New Bhadrapur Road', 'Kupondole', 'Bagmati', 'Lalitpur/Patan', 'Nepal', 'Narayan Wagle', '9851139592', 'fom@hotelhimalaya.com.np', ' http://hotelhimalaya.com.np/', 'Situated in the epicenter of Kathmandu valley, offering great value for money with superb rooms and a wonderful dining experience. Come and stay with us and allow us to make you feel at home with true Nepalese hospitability!\r\n', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<div class=\"overview-img\">\r\n			<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/birtamod-restaurant.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b>Spirit Bar</b>:</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Spirit Bar Serves you margarita and tequila with the best tanta Zing atmosphere to your time with capacity of 20 Pax.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			6 Dinning Outlet Including Cabin and Bar.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			24 Hours service</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<b>Specialty</b></p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Mostly people visit our property to have a best Food quality and for our great service. Which we provide <strong>&quot;Hospitality from the Heart&quot;</strong></p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Siddhartha Hotel Grand City, located in the heart of Birtamod, Jhapa, is a welcoming 3-star hotel that offers a comfortable and convenient stay for both business and leisure travelers. With a range of amenities and a prime location, this hotel provides an excellent base for exploring the charming town of Birtamod and its surroundings.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			The hotel&#39;s strategic location opens up exciting opportunities for exploration. The area is renowned for cycling, making it an ideal destination for cycling enthusiasts. Additionally, car hire services are available on-site, allowing you to conveniently explore the area at your own pace.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Our 48 well-equipped rooms include Deluxe and Super Deluxe rooms, as well as interconnecting, quad, and junior suite rooms.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/birtamod-overview.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	Relax in elegance at our hotel pool before enjoying a cocktail and meal of your choosing at our Spirit bar. The Siddhartha Hotel in Birtamod is also a great location for weddings and conferences. Both Mechi Hall and Koshi Hall can accommodate 400 persons. Our magnificent Board Rooms are an excellent choice for any meeting, conference, event, or seminars.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2021-08-25', 0, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 19, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3566.2186535207106!2d87.98759317444797!3d26.641480776809836!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39e5bb518a9db4b5%3A0xa6189e2b500024ae!2sSiddhartha%20Hotel%20Grand%20City!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1702630135667!5m2!1sen!2snp', 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/NpuPNixFdtS1W3ae8', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '', '', 'The Hotel is located at the heart of the bustling city of Birtamod in Jhapa district in the Province 1. ', '23', '', '', 'Yes', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'birtamod', 'fT3GUG'),
