(11, 3, 161, 'Siddhartha Sunny Resort, Surkhet', '503346', 'Siddhartha Sunny Resort, Surkhet', 'siddhartha-sunny-resort-surkhet', '3vdU4t', '', 'Hotel & Resort', 37, '', 'YTowOnt9', 'YLSjH-ags03246_1_1.jpg', 'K9kdl-surkhet_thumb.jpg', '', '083-520922, 9858051660', '083-520922, 9858051660', '083-520922, 9858051660', 'srskt@siddharthahospitality.com', 'srskt@siddharthahospitality.com', 'srskt@siddharthahospitality.com', '', 0, 'Birendranagar-03, surkhet', '', '', '', 'Nepal', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<div class=\"overview-img\">\r\n			<img src=\"/userfiles/images/surkhet_restaurant.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-12\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Enjoy the diverse and convenient culinary offerings available at our hotel. Our on-site restaurants cater to all tastes and appetites, with The Fun Caf&eacute; and The Coffee Shop serving up delicious dishes from breakfast to dinner. For a serene dining experience, head to our rooftop restaurant, The Terrace Garden.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Satisfy your sweet tooth with delightful treats at The Pastry Shop or unwind with your preferred beverage at The Lobby Bar. For those who prefer dining in the privacy of their own room, we offer 24-hour room service.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Dine inside amidst the luxurious ambience or simply enjoy dining at the Garden, which is designed to give you an experience of feel Joy, relax able &amp; Comfortable.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			<strong>Opening Hours:</strong> Bar open from morning 10 am To 10 Pm (24 Hour room service for in-house guest)</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Maya restaurant Open for 24 hours.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			The Sunny Resort is situated in Surkhet, the capital of the Karnali Province, which is both a bustling town and a place of historical significance. The 12th-century Kakre Bihar (a Buddhist temple), Bulbule Taal (lake), Deauti Bajai, a Hindu temple, and Gothi Daha (lake) are some of the prominent landmarks of the city. As the name suggests Sunny Resort is the only a 4-star hotel in Karnali Pradesh and finds itself amid open space. The Resort offers a variety of facilities including a gymnasium, a spa, and a swimming pool. In addition to this, the Resort&rsquo;s fruit garden not only accentuates the beauty of the resort but also offers fresh and seasonal fruits to its clients.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Siddhartha Sunny Resort, Surkhet has a garden, shared lounge, a restaurant and bar in Neta. The property has room service and a 24-hour front desk for guests. The resort will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, a safety deposit box, a TV, a terrace and a shared bathroom with a shower. Siddhartha Sunny Resort, Surkhet provides some accommodations with mountain views, and the rooms have a balcony. All rooms have a closet.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			The nearest airport is Nepalganj Airport, 62 miles from the accommodation.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/surket-restaurant.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2021-09-29', 1, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 17, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3502.996494518932!2d81.59228007453483!3d28.599881975682607!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x39a288a8313ce97d%3A0xf8bd145a7a787f9e!2sSiddhartha%20Sunny%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1702629744460!5m2!1sen!2snp', '', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '<div class=\"row 