(20, 5, 194, 'Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort', '503210', 'Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort', 'siddhartha-vilasa-banbas-resort', 'fr5rYZ', '', 'Hotel & Resort', 12, '', '', 'VbAMP-dsc04745_hdr_1.jpg', 'gfQuI-vilasa_front.jpg', '', '9851147802', '9851147802', '9851147802', 'snripesh@siddharthabiz.com', 'snripesh@siddharthabiz.com', 'snripesh@siddharthabiz.com', '', 0, 'Khairahani-13 harnari ', '', '', '', 'Nepal', '', '', '', '', '', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort features a multi-cuisine restaurant where you can savor a variety of delicious dishes. Whether you&#39;re enjoying a meal or a drink at the bar, you can immerse yourself in the tranquil surroundings while indulging in exquisite culinary experiences.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	The multi-cuisine bar and restaurant at Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort is not just a place to eat; it&#39;s a culinary and cultural journey that celebrates the local Tharu heritage and showcases the beauty of Nepal&#39;s wilderness. From locally sourced ingredients to traditional Tharu decor and captivating wildlife views, it offers a dining experience like no other. Guests can savor the flavors of the region, immerse themselves in local culture, and connect with nature&mdash;all while enjoying the comfort and luxury of this remarkable resort. It&#39;s a place where dining becomes an unforgettable adventure.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n			Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort seamlessly integrates the modern world with the untamed beauty of the wilderness. With 23 individually designed villas with 34 room, 1 multi-cuisine restaurant, a courtyard, two conference halls, a bar, and a sparkling swimming pool, the resort is thoughtfully designed to provide the utmost comfort while preserving the natural landscape. It covers a vast area of 3.5 bighas, ensuring that guests have ample space to explore and unwind.</p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n			<strong>A Villa in the Wilderness</strong></p>\r\n		<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n			Each villa at Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort is a secluded sanctuary, meticulously designed to immerse guests in the authentic charm of the region. Locally sourced materials adorn the interiors, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The spacious rooms are bathed in natural sunlight, and large windows frame breathtaking views of the verdant jungle. Guests are invited to unwind in the lap of luxury while feeling connected to the natural world just beyond their doorstep.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/vilasa-overview.jpg\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>A Natural Symphony of Birds and Wildlife</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	One of the resort&#39;s most captivating features is its proximity to the Chitwan National Park. From the restaurant and various vantage points within the resort, guests can witness the wonders of the park. The restaurant not only serves delectable cuisine but also offers a unique dining experience where you can watch animals from the national park and beautiful birds in their natural habitat. It&#39;s an exceptional opportunity for birdwatching enthusiasts and wildlife lovers to be surrounded by the sights and sounds of nature.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>The Tranquil Pond</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	A centerpiece of tranquility within the resort is the shimmering pond. Surrounded by lush foliage, it provides a serene backdrop for relaxation and reflection. Whether you&#39;re enjoying a quiet moment by the water&#39;s edge or simply watching native birds take flight over the pond, this oasis within an oasis serves as a gentle reminder of the beauty and serenity of nature. It&#39;s the perfect spot to unwind, meditate, or simply reconnect with the natural world.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	<strong>Activities and Adventures</strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Aside from the tranquil experiences within the resort, Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas offers an array of activities and adventures for guests to explore the surrounding jungle. Guided safaris into the Chitwan National Park allow you to get up close and personal with the diverse wildlife that calls this region home. You can also take part in cultural excursions to nearby villages, fishing facilities inside resort and. offering a glimpse into the local way of life.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n	Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort is more than just a place to stay; it&#39;s an immersive journey into the heart of nature&#39;s wonders. With its luxurious accommodations, breathtaking views, and proximity to the Chitwan National Park, it offers a unique opportunity to experience the wild beauty of Nepal while enjoying the comforts of a world-class resort. Whether you&#39;re a nature enthusiast, a birdwatcher, or simply seeking a peaceful retreat, this resort promises an extraordinary escape into the embrace of the jungle. It&#39;s a place where the modern world gracefully converges with the untamed beauty of the wilderness, creating memories that will last a lifetime.</p>\r\n', '2023-10-08', 0, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 10, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '', '', 'Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort seamlessly integrates the modern world with the untamed beauty of the wilderness. ', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'https://www.facebook.com/SiddharthaVilasaBanbas', '', '', 'HotelResort', 'yhtlif'),
