(24, 3, 178, 'S Cafe\' Manmohan, Kathmandu', '', 'S Cafe\' Manmohan, Kathmandu', 's-cafe-manmohan-kathmandu', 'aqZx9Q', '', 'Cafe', 10, '', '', 'VXt05-img_8083_1.jpg', '4juMd-scafe_1.jpg', '', '9851332015', '9851332015', '9851332015', 'scafe@siddharthahospitality.com', 'scafe@siddharthahospitality.com', 'scafe@siddharthahospitality.com', '', 0, 'Manmohan Building-Maharajgunj', '', '', '', 'Nepal', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		We serve a variety of delicious bakery items like cakes, pastries, breads etc. We also have sweets, soft meals, office lunch boxes and beverages.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"room-outer\">\r\n	<div class=\"row feature-slider\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_8232.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/cuisine.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/cake8.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/cuisine2.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Indulge in the delectable array of breads and pastries we offer, featuring buttery croissants, flaky danishes, and irresistible cinnamon rolls.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"room-outer\">\r\n	<div class=\"row feature-slider\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/bread.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/pasteries.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/pasteries2.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/pasteries1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Celebrate sweet moments with your loved ones by savoring custom-ordered cakes and an array of delectable sweets from Scafe, ensuring a delightful time with a diverse selection of indulgent treats.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"room-outer\">\r\n	<div class=\"row feature-slider\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/cake9.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/cake4.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/sweets15.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/sweets1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Satisfy every seasonal craving with our versatile beverage offerings &ndash; from comforting hot coffees on chilly days to refreshing iced drinks perfect for summer.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"room-outer\">\r\n	<div class=\"row feature-slider\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_8171.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_8203.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_8174.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_8165.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality (SBGH) a leading hospitality chain of Nepal. Successfully running a host of Hotels,resorts &amp; restaurants is now in to the operation of a chain of cafes. Name of Siddhartha sweetS &amp; Bakery (Scafe) under the banner of SBGH. The Caf&eacute; is Owned by the employee of SBGH to endorse face that the&nbsp; staffs of SBGH are not merely employees,but the owners of the group in the real sense . Scafe has come into existence to meet up with the ever soaring demand of coffee, bakery and fast foods which are popular among the youths and professional, today.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Scafe is established to cater to the taste- buds of the coffee lover who are looking for a light meal or ready- to- go- food at reasonable price in an informal setup with a swift service at every point of time.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			Scafe also focuses on serving its esteemed clients with taste and hygienic indian sweets varieties which are not only popular among us rather integral to our festivals and auspicious occasions.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			&nbsp;</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/IMG_8090.jpg\" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2023-10-08', 0, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 6, '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '', '', 'Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality (SBGH) a leading hospitality chain of Nepal. ', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'SCAFE', '10'),
