bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/sweets13.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '', '<div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		Cater to your every seasonal desire with our adaptable selection of beverages &ndash; enjoy warming hot coffees during cooler days or relish in the cool refreshment of iced drinks ideal for the summer heat.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"room-outer\">\r\n	<div class=\"row feature-slider\">\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/beverage18.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/beverage19.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/beverage20.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"col-md-3 col-sm-6 col-xs-12 mar-bottom-30\">\r\n			<div class=\"room-item\">\r\n				<div class=\"room-image\">\r\n					<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/beverage17.jpg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality (SBGH) a leading hospitality chain of Nepal. Successfully running a host of Hotels,resorts &amp; restaurants is now in to the operation of a chain of cafes. Name of Siddhartha sweetS &amp; Bakery (Scafe) under the banner of SBGH. The Caf&eacute; is Owned by the employee of SBGH to endorse face that the&nbsp; staffs of SBGH are not merely employees,but the owners of the group in the real sense . Scafe has come into existence to meet up with the ever soaring demand of coffee, bakery and fast foods which are popular among the youths and professional, today.<br />\r\n			Scafe is established to cater to the taste- buds of the coffee lover who are looking for a light meal or ready- to- go- food at reasonable price in an informal setup with a swift service at every point of time.<br />\r\n			Scafe also focuses on serving its esteemed clients with taste and hygienic indian sweets varieties which are not only popular among us rather integral to our festivals and auspicious occasions.</p>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/AGS02792.jpg\" style=\"border-radius: 10px;\" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2023-10-08', 0, 3, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 5, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3520.6610964957786!2d81.62163777451056!3d28.06537077597916!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x399867403e1b1dcf%3A0x645ec299b11ad8ea!2sSiddhartha%20Sweets%20%26%20Bakery!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1702637065229!5m2!1sen!2snp', 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/TgPt5uALouCRN8kR8', '', '', '', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAxIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjI7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAyIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO31pOjM7YToyOntzOjg6InF1ZXN0aW9uIjtzOjU6IkZBUSAzIjtzOjY6ImFuc3dlciI7czowOiIiO319', 'YTozOntpOjE7YToxOntzOjU6InRpdGxlIjtzOjg6IlBvbGljeSAxIjt9aToyO2E6MTp7czo1OiJ0aXRsZSI7czo4OiJQb2xpY3kgMiI7fWk6MzthOjE6e3M6NToidGl0bGUiO3M6ODoiUG9saWN5IDMiO319', '', '', '', '', 'Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality (SBGH) a leading hospitality chain of Nepal. ', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'SCAFE', '11'),
