(28, 0, 175, 'Siddhatha Hotel Lumbini Green, Lamahi', '503350', 'Siddhatha Hotel Lumbini Green, Lamahi', 'siddhatha-hotel-lumbini-green-lamahi', 'm6M2tQ', '', 'Hotel & Resort', 44, '', '', 'xXPaq-untitled_1.jpg', 'a8K2n-peace_nepalgunj.jpg', '', '082-417072, 9857876555', '082-417072, 9857876555', '082-417072, 9857876555', 'lamahi@siddharthahospitality.com', 'test@siddhartha.com', 'test@siddhartha.com', '', 0, 'Lamahi, 05- Dang', '', '', '', 'Nepal', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '<div class=\"row\">\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<p>\r\n			As the name suggests, Siddhartha Hotel Lumbini Green Lamahi is situated at Lamahi Bazar of Dang district close to the East-West Highway. This modern hotel stands amid spacious lush green environs with adult and children swimming pools, poolside open view restaurant and ample parking space. The hotel also offers health club facilities. A spa is under construction now.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			The hotel has 17 rooms, ranging from standard to deluxe, restaurants (Bar and Poolside) and private dining rooms (PDR).</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			The hotel is 111 km away from Kohalpur, 26 km from Bhaluwang and 121 km from Butwal.</p>\r\n		<p>\r\n			It is an ideal destination for all types of guests, from leisure and laidback stay to business and conferences as well as partying and social events.</p>\r\n		<div>\r\n			&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n		<img src=\"/userfiles/files/Untitled-2(1).jpg\" style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" /></div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '2023-10-12', 0, 0, '', '', 1, '', '', 0, 1, 0, '', '', 2, '', '', 'https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3526.8966905049956!2d82.51321386560471!3d27.874443701756725!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x399799024c212f49%3A0x86cc4d182c5382db!2sSiddhartha%20Hotel%20Green%20Lumbini!5e0!3m2!1sen!2snp!4v1702630617629!5m2!1sen!2snp', 'https://maps.app.goo.gl/itDmVHvfsYN2eRxa9', '', '', '', 'Y