(1, 'siddhartha-business-group-of-br-hospitality-pvt-ltd', 'SIDDHARTHA Business Group of<br/>Hospitality Pvt. Ltd', '<p>\r\n	Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality is a major enterprise in Nepal, renowned for its diverse portfolio of businesses that includes hotels, training institute, bakeries, a hospitality trade center, and an ongoing expansion into the world of luxurious hotels and resorts. SBGH has effectively solidified its position as a premier and highly-regarded brand within the hospitality industry of Nepal, earning a distinguished reputation for its excellence and innovation.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	SBGH has not only excelled in food and lodging services but has also emerged as a significant player contributing to the national economy. With 17 entities under its umbrella, including 15 hotels and resorts, restaurants, cafes, training institutes, and a hospitality trade center, SBGH has been a transformative force in the hospitality sector, making substantial contributions to the country&#39;s economic growth.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	Siddhartha Business Group has been able to set a benchmark in the industry itself. We are the one stop solution for all classes of hospitality services you are looking for. From the normal cafe to luxurious hotel experience we have got you by far the best service to you. There is always something new in store for our customer, be it adventure or an extraordinary experience that you will experience nowhere.</p>\r\n', 1, '', '', 0, '2016-08-20 15:28:12', 1, 1, 0x613a313a7b693a303b733a32343a22444f645a352d64736330373038335f6864725f322e6a7067223b7d, '', ''),
