(9, 'history', 'History', '<section class=\"about-counter\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"main-timeline mt-5\">\r\n			<!-- 1998 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								1998</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality today evolved from a modest fast food stall in Tikapur town (now Tikapur Municipality) in Kailali district in the Sudoor Paschim (Far-West) Province. Its maiden food stall was established on 5 February 1998. The food stall was credited for introducing exotic dishes, the momos and the chowmein (stick noodles) in Tikapur which were yet new to the local residents.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 1999 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								1999</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								With the growing popularity of the fast-food stall the company soon ventured onto a small guest house named Himal Guest House with merely 9 rooms. As the town was repositioning itself into a bustling hub with increased exigencies of businessmen, traders, agro-based enterprises, NGOs, educational institutions and many more, the prospect for a full-fledged guest house was reassuring. On 16 June 1999 Himal Guest House completely transformed into a multi-facility business hotel named Siddhartha Guest House.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2001 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2001</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								With the turn of the new century, SBGH introduced one of a kind cottage style restaurant in Nepalgunj at Surkhet Road.Siddhartha Cottage is town&#39;s most luxurious restaurant. The cottage is unique in its architecture and resplendent with wide open terrace and spacious rooms. The cottage provides fine dining set-ups, private rooms, a bar, banquet halls and separate vegetarian and non-vegetarian restaurants as well. It is regarded as one of the best outlets for wedding and other auspicious occasions.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n					<div class=\"card\">\r\n						<img alt=\"image\" src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/siddhartha_cottage_nepalgunj.jpg\" /></div>\r\n				</div>\r\n				<img class=\"left\" src=\"\" /></div>\r\n			<!-- 2002 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2002</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								SBGH asserted their presence in the heart of capital city with Hotel Siddhartha, Sundhara. Located next to the city&#39;s towering edifice, the Dharahara and a stone&#39;s throw away from the Tundikhel, the national military parade grounds, a guest can stroll around the landmarks and heritage sites of the old Kathmandu within few minutes. This is also an ideal address both for business and recreation as the Hotel stands in the middle of business landmarks such as government offices, shopping malls, multiplexes, cinema halls etc.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2004 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2004</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								Adding to the list of cottage style restaurants, SBGH started Siddhartha Cottage Restaurant and Bar, Tinkune which is the first of its kind in the Kathmandu valley. Just a couple of kilometers away from Nepal&rsquo;s only international airport, the Cottage is a multi-facility eatery that boasts traditional bamboo cottages, fine dining rooms, stylish bar as well as meeting, conference and banquet halls. The Cottage serves delectable Nepali, Indian and continental foods at very reasonable price. It is also worth mentioning that the Cottage has ample parking space for 30-40 four-wheelers.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2008 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2008</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								Spread over 2.5 acres of landscaped grounds, SBGH established Hotel Siddhartha Nepalgunj, a luxury four-star hotel in bustling town of Nepalgunj. Situated at the city&rsquo;s vibrant center near shopping and business landmarks, our hotel offers five-star service accentuated with deluxe amenities such as fitness center, swimming pool, health club, badminton court etc. The hotel boasts spacious, 125 well-appointed rooms and suites with free Wi-Fi.The Hotel is an ideal venue for workshop, seminar, party as it boasts conference rooms, banquet hall, swimming pool and ample parking space.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2009 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2009</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								This year SBGH commenced the Riverside Resort of Chisapani. This is an ideal place to escape the scorching heat of Terai and to rejuvenate in nature&rsquo;s wilderness. Riverside Resort, as the name implies, situated on the banks of the Karnali River offers an array of activities, from boating to jungle safari or simply reposing in the opulence of nature sipping beer with fresh water fishes from the river.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2011 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2011</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								SBGH established Siddhartha Cottage Restaurant,Dhobighat,Lalitpur. Given its proximity with bustling food hub of Jhamsikhel (or Jhamel), the Cottage is an address for all food lovers, party-goers and corporate executives for recreation, conference and banquets.The Cottage offers fine dining set-ups and open space gathering facilities for corporate and social events. The Cottage is easily accessible from Patan Durbar Square, Labim Mall Pulchowk and National Zoo.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2012 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2012</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								Siddhartha Cottage Restaurant, Butwal (Estd. 2012) is Situated in the bustling town of Butwal, Siddhartha Cottage is just 40 minutes&#39; drive (22 Km) from Gautam Buddha International Airport and 30 minutes&#39; drive (22Km) from Sonauli border. Likewise, Lumbini, the birthplace of Lord Buddha is just an hour&#39;s drive (42 Km). The Cottage offers indoor-cum-outdoor ambience amid lush green open space and water fountain.Be it family gatherings or friendly reunion or office seminar, you can spend your quality time relishing tantalizing foods in the opulence of nature.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2015 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2015</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								SBGH started the only luxurious 4 star property in Karnali Pradesh. The Sunny Resort is situated in Surkhet, the capital of the Karnali Province, which is both a bustling town and a place of historical significance. The 12th-century Kakre Bihar (a Buddhist temple), Bulbule Taal (lake), Deauti Bajai, a Hindu temple, and Gothi Daha (lake) are some of the prominent landmarks of the city. As the name suggests Sunny Resort is the only a 4-star hotel in Karnali Pradesh and finds itself amid open space. The Resort offers a variety of facilities including a gymnasium, a spa, and a swimming pool. In addition to this, the Resort&#39;s fruit garden not only accentuates the beauty of the resort but also offers fresh and seasonal fruits to its clients.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2016 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2016</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								In 2016, a new resort was added to SBGH&#39;s list of joyful haven. Situated on the banks of the gushing Trisuli River on Prithvi Highway in Chumlingtar village of Chitwan district which is less than three-hours&#39; comfortable drive from Kathmandu, Siddhartha Riverside Resort is an ideal retreat for everyone either lazing at the resort or engaging in outdoor activities or adventures. Tucked away few minutes from the Mankamana Cable Car station at Kurintar, this Resort is a perfect destination for those who want to pay homage to Goddess Manakamana (the wish-fulfilling-deity) while languishing in the opulence of waters and lush green surroundings. The Resort offers every recreational facility such as Swimming Pool, Spa, Camp/Bonfire, Live BBQ, Village Hiking, among others.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2019 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2019</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								SBGH moved further west with it&#39;s new operation, Siddhartha Hotel New Anand, Kanchanpur. Hotel is located ideally in the far-west of Nepal, rising splendid over the adventure landscape of Sudurpaschim Province. Hotel new anand provides cozy accommodation with superior service, offering quick access to national park and cultural heritages.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2020 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2020</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								SBGH ventured into a new destination inside Kathmandu with Siddhartha Botique Hotel, Boudha. Siddhartha Boutique Hotel guarantees a heady atmosphere and a delightful time in the warm environment. We value modern amenities with a dash of traditional Nepalese hospitality. A poolside restaurant, event spaces, ample parking, a swimming pool, a gym, and a spa are among the hotel&#39;s amenities. The hotel is located 1.7 kilometers from the Bouddhanath Stupa and 3.8 kilometers from the Pashupatinath Temple. The nearest airport is Tribhuvan International Airport, which is 4 kilometers away.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2021 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2021</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								In this year, we spread our hospitality to the beautiful city of Birtamod. Located at the heart of Birtamod with a contemporary room and modernamenities, the hotel is a perfect venue for leisure and business travellers.It is approximately 30 minutes and 15 minutes driving distance from Nepal-India border, Kakarvitta and Bhadrapur Airport respectively. The hotel consists of all the facilities that a customers seek to have a comfortable stay.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2022 overview -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2022</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10 order-md-1\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								Since the establishment of fast-food stall in Tikapur, SBGH over the glorious twenty-five years has 21 outlets , ranging from budget to five-star (Bhairahawa), from Mahendra Nagar in the far-west to Birtamod in the far-east, that include hotel and resorts, restaurants, cafes, party banquets, sweet and bakery and trading business. There are many more in the offing.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2022 lumbini green -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2022</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								This year SBGH established a lavish and elegant resort,Siddhartha Lumbini Green Resort, situated in the town of Chandrauta, Shivraj-2 in Kapilvastu district.As the name itself suggests, the Resort is resplendent in the Pagoda style architecture amid lush green environs and fresh-water pools, covering 16 acres of land. The Resort is designed in a rural setting as a testimony of agro-tourism, with vegetable farm and fishing ponds. Nevertheless, the Resort offers all modern amenities at par with the modern lifestyles. Most importantly, the Resort is opulent with the thematic Water Park boasting a swimming pool, a very spacious and well facilitated spa and a gymnasium. Hence, it is an ideal destination for all types of guests, from leisure and laidback stay to business and conferences as well as partying and destination weddings.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2022 nuwakot -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline left\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2 order-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2022</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								Adding to the list of properties, SBGH commenced Hotel Siddhartha Water, located in Battar Bazar, adjacent to the main bus park of Bidur Municipality, the district headquarters of Nuwakot district. The Hotel sprawling over one acres of land possesses ample space and lush green garden with soothing sound of the Trishuli River flowing beneath it. The Hotel offers a selection of rooms; Suite, Deluxe, Standard and Friends, befitting the choice of the guests.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<!-- 2023 -->\r\n			<div class=\"timeline right\">\r\n				<div class=\"card\">\r\n					<div class=\"card-body row\">\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-2\">\r\n							<h3>\r\n								2023</h3>\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"col-md-10\">\r\n							<p class=\"mb-0\">\r\n								This year SBGH celebrated its Silver-Jubilee celebrations in Bhairahawa amid huge fanfare. SBGH also started a 5-star resort at Khairahani-13 Harnari, named Siddhartha Vilasa Banbas Resort, seamlessly integrating the modern world with the untamed beauty of wilderness.</p>\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 1, '', '', 0, '2023-11-19 16:05:05', 8, 0, 0x613a303a7b7d, '', ''),
(8, 'privacy-policies', 'Privacy policies', '<p>\r\n	SIDDHARTHA Business Group of Hospitality (SBGH) is a hospitality enterprise focused in food and hospitality as well as travel and trade. Hence, SBGH has surpassed its services from fooding and lodging to a prominent hospitality enterprise engaging in an array of activities that help bolster national economy. With twenty-five years of experience in restaurant.</p>\r\n', 1, '', '', 0, '2023-11-02 12:16:28', 7, 0, 0x613a303a7b7d, '', ''),
(10, 'message-from-chairman', 'Message from Chairman', '<!-- counter Ends --><!-- about team starts-->\r\n<section class=\"about-team \">\r\n	<div class=\"container mt-5\">\r\n		<div class=\"row\">\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-3 d-flex justify-content-center justify-content-md-start \">\r\n				<div class=\"team-image mb-3\" style=\"    width: 235px;\r\n    height: 270px;\r\n    background: #d8d8d8;\">\r\n					<img src=\"/assets/userfiles/files/1622888917462%20(1).jpeg\" /></div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div class=\"col-md-9\">\r\n				<div class=\"team-content\">\r\n					<p>\r\n						<strong>Dear Friends and Partners,</strong></p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						It is with immense pride and gratitude that I stand before you today as the Chairman of the largest hospitality chain in Nepal. Our journey began in the charming town of Tikapur in 1998 with a simple yet powerful vision - to provide exceptional hospitality experiences that would not only showcase the beauty of Nepal but also uplift the lives of its people.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						Over the course of 25 incredible years, we have transformed that vision into a reality, touching the lives of countless individuals, both within and beyond our organization. Today, we proudly employ more than 1500 talented individuals who are the heart and soul of our hospitality chain. Their dedication, passion, and commitment have been instrumental in our remarkable growth and success.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						Our journey has been one of evolution and innovation. We have continuously strived to raise the bar in the hospitality industry, providing our guests with experiences that are not only memorable but also authentic. From our humble beginnings in Tikapur, we have expanded our footprint across Nepal, welcoming guests from all corners of the globe.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						As we celebrate our achievements, we are also looking forward to the exciting future that lies ahead. We are in the process of diversifying our portfolio to offer an even wider range of experiences, ensuring that we remain at the forefront of Nepal&#39;s vibrant hospitality industry. Our commitment to excellence, sustainability, and community engagement remains unwavering, and we are excited to share our new ventures with you in the coming years.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						None of this would have been possible without the trust and support of our valued guests, partners, and stakeholders. Your belief in us has been the driving force behind our growth, and for that, we are truly grateful.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						At our core, we remain deeply rooted in the values that have guided us since day one - a commitment to Nepal&#39;s rich culture and natural beauty, a dedication to the welfare of our team members, and a passion for creating extraordinary memories for our guests.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						I invite you to join us on this continued journey of growth, exploration, and innovation. Together, we will create experiences that transcend borders and enrich lives.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						Thank you for being a part of our story, and we look forward to welcoming you to the world of our hospitality.</p>\r\n					<p>\r\n						Warm regards,<br />\r\n						<strong>Chintamani Neupane</strong><br />\r\n						Chairman, Siddhartha Business Group of Hospitality</p>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</section>\r\n<!-- about team Ends -->', 1, '', '', 0, '2023-11-19 16:05:41', 9, 0, 0x613a303a7b7d, '', ''),
